game.name: Girls Winter Fun
game.description:
Hey girls! Where are you? Your favorite and the most gorgeous princesses are planning to have some seasonal fun. Yes, the winter has just begun and these two beautiful princesses have already decided to get involved in the winter holiday skiing. The best part is that they have already reached on the mountaintop. All you need to do is help them to pick up the best ski costumes to make their trip successful in Girls Winter Fun. Be careful and try to be fast since girls are eagerly waiting for you!

Start with the little girl by guiding her to choose the nice ski outfit in this brand new girls game! Dress her up with green and orange jacket with pink fur on the side and combine it up with a snowboard with pink hearts and a lovely pair of plaid red shoes and warm boots! Complete her look with some elegant girl-girly accessories! Now move on to her elder sister who also wants to look perfect in this HTML5 dressing game.

Give her a green jacket with an awesome butterfly print and combine her look with a pair of cute jeans, a green hat and a pair of warm boots! Make sure to complete her look with an elegant hat, gloves and other needful ski equipment. Give her a raspberry pink sleigh. Hey ladies! It looks now they are ready now to hit the slopes! Feel free to dress them up with the colorful skirts, padded vests and leggings and combine their look with bunny ears!
